Enum-Klasse StrategyOpponent

java.lang.Object
java.lang.Enum<StrategyOpponent>
model.StrategyOpponent
Alle implementierten Schnittstellen:
Serializable, Comparable<StrategyOpponent>, Constable
public enum StrategyOpponent extends Enum<StrategyOpponent>
Represents the strategy of the opponent in terms of the level of aggressiveness and defensiveness.

1 corresponds to low, 2 to middle, 3 to high.
